		"description": "Complete API collection for SRMS (Service Request Management System)\n\nBase URL: http://192.168.68.61:8000/api\n\n## Authentication\nThis API uses Laravel Sanctum bearer tokens.\n\n### How to use:\n1. Test public APIs without authentication\n2. Use 'Auth - Send OTP' and 'Auth - Verify OTP' to get a bearer token\n3. Set the token in the collection variable 'auth_token'\n4. Authenticated requests will automatically include the token",
